{"tid":2490830,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"丈夫出軌妻1元怒拍賣《遊戲王》卡洩憤，最後拍出2000萬!!!","createTime":"2021-04-16T01:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T04:44:51.000Z","uid":253829,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ac8bc64016bcdcec24bca3cf860fdfdee0ad938d","tid":2490830,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:55:24.000Z","msg":"文章來源：<a href=\"http://Qooah.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FQooah.com&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=dd2017e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Qooah.com</a><br />\n<br />\n作為遊戲的又一理財級產品《遊戲王》卡牌，應該是不少骨灰級玩家們的寶貝收藏。這些卡牌的價格也早就超過其原來的價值，而近日在日本一個拍賣網站上卻有拍賣者以1日元的低價起拍上架了一整套遊戲王卡盒，商品信息欄內還有她描述的拍賣故事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.1XWDQ7rbK0Jz9CV94pXdg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMS42O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/w4UHsmP48dBPEK.gEofELw--~B/aD02Mjc7dz0xMjAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/iloveapps.com/2a2ad77c6c4bb2a8f81cec4c2e0c417d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.1XWDQ7rbK0Jz9CV94pXdg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMS42O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fw4UHsmP48dBPEK.gEofELw--~B%2FaD02Mjc7dz0xMjAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Filoveapps.com%2F2a2ad77c6c4bb2a8f81cec4c2e0c417d&h=b0f78a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據拍賣網顯示，拍賣者是這些卡牌收藏玩家的妻子，她表示因自己的丈夫出軌，其抱持著報復的心態一舉將丈夫還未開封的遊戲王卡以1日元的價格放上了拍賣網。她透露自己其實不懂卡牌，但自己清楚丈夫對這些卡牌視如珍寶，所以這些卡牌就成了她反擊丈夫出軌的致命點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KXViw67HHf8FQ90GWZY50g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ3OS4yODg4ODg4ODg4ODg5O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Xq6k25.mYm9xLgr0T3Y_tw--~B/aD02NzQ7dz0xMzUwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/iloveapps.com/d20a53225f3c39227b1a553e69478b9f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FKXViw67HHf8FQ90GWZY50g--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ3OS4yODg4ODg4ODg4ODg5O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FXq6k25.mYm9xLgr0T3Y_tw--~B%2FaD02NzQ7dz0xMzUwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Filoveapps.com%2Fd20a53225f3c39227b1a553e69478b9f&h=4cc0814a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從這位妻子的卡牌圖片看到，她丈夫收集的卡牌較齊全，顯眼處擺放著的還是稀有卡，以1日元的價格擺出來拍賣未免太可惜。不過好在網友們非常識貨，價格已經被炒起來了，最終拍賣價格飆升到2050萬日元左右。<br />\n<br />\n原定拍賣從2021年4月10日開始，持續至2021年4月18日，不過最後在4月14日已經被結束完成拍賣。"},{"pid":"709d673bf2b23245fcee45d6d725c1d32bae8eec","tid":2490830,"uid":65747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:56:25.000Z","msg":"個男人會唔會又殺左個老婆"},{"pid":"e651dc3ce580e7f66b3074aa5c3495670ce7f850","tid":2490830,"uid":35317,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:58:57.000Z","msg":"公開買賣贓物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買家賣家都要坐監"},{"pid":"3a1fa5cd6e66a0dba2ea2aea7df15f669895ac06","tid":2490830,"uid":73095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e651dc3ce580e7f66b3074aa5c3495670ce7f850","tid":2490830,"uid":35317,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:58:57.000Z","msg":"公開買賣贓物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買家賣家都要坐監"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:05:20.000Z","msg":"日本既法律 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e9eb7885f4ae0c723fecd0e60a9541f246c4f4","tid":2490830,"uid":189638,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e651dc3ce580e7f66b3074aa5c3495670ce7f850","tid":2490830,"uid":35317,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:58:57.000Z","msg":"公開買賣贓物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買家賣家都要坐監"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:34:53.000Z","msg":"兩條柒頭結咗婚，屋企嘅物資就係共有財嚟。即係老婆賣咗張sofa，當然可以拗，但解決唔到，法官都會幫你分身家。<br />\n<br />\n結婚前自己諗清楚好過自己幻想咁叫贓物。<br />\n<br />\n結婚唔係簽張紙咁簡